### Test Integrity (Prevents FAIL_TEST_BROKEN)
- [ ] Tests **ONLY use public API** - no internal/private attribute access
- [ ] Tests **never recreate internal sentinels** (e.g., no mock objects for library sentinels)
- [ ] Tests **import only exported items** - verified exports exist before writing tests
