- [ ] test.sh is **executable (mode 100755)** in patch
- [ ] test.sh base passes (existing tests unaffected)
- [ ] test.sh new **fails with meaningful errors** (not syntax/import errors)
- [ ] test.patch contains **only test files** (no source code modifications)
- [ ] Challenge difficulty: **HARD** for AI evaluators
- [ ] Multiple valid implementation approaches possible
